# Cursor Configuration for NSS Portal

## CSS and Tailwind CSS
- Recognize @tailwind directives as valid CSS
- Accept @keyframes as valid CSS at-rules
- Allow rgba() color functions
- Accept modern CSS syntax

## File Associations
*.css = tailwindcss

## Linting Rules
- Disable CSS validation warnings for Tailwind directives
- Accept modern CSS properties and values
- Allow alpha values in colors (rgba, rgb with alpha)
- Accept kebab-case and camelCase in keyframes
- Allow duplicate selectors when needed
- Accept shorthand and longhand properties
